    <!-- Rules and Policy -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col s12 min-div-width">
            <ul class="collection with-header">
                <li class="collection-header">
                    <a class="rules-anchor" id="house"></a>
                    <h4 class="center headline">
                        <strong>House Rules and Policy</strong>
                    </h4>
                </li>
                <li class="collection-item">Your room number denotes your shelf number in the fridge and pantry.</li>
                <li class="collection-item">Lock the door upon leaving and entering the home to keep our guests and property safe.</li>
                <li class="collection-item">Do not flush any paper towels, feminine products, kleenex, napkins, or other trash down the toilet. Bath
                Tissue only!</li>
                <li class="collection-item">Do not move the AC unit, this may cause damage to the air vent.</li>
                <li class="collection-item">Clean up after yourself in the kitchen (dishes, utensils, pots, and pans) and in the bathroom(shave trimmmings).</li>
                <li class="collection-item">The hand towels in the bathrooms are for drying clean hands only. Please wash your hands thoroughly first.</li>
                <li class="collection-item">Keep all your food items in your designated shelves.</li>
                <li class="collection-item">No overnight guests without authorization.</li>
                <li class="collection-item">Use the trash bins next to the driveway for disposal of large items.</li>
                <li class="collection-item">No loud noise after 10pm or before 9am.</li>
                <li class="collection-item"><b>NEVER</b> go over the balcony railing since the wooden trellis is very fragile.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
