                    <h4 class="center headline">
                        <strong>Check out Tips</strong>
                    </h4>
                </li>
                <li class="collection-item">Check out time is 11am.</li>
                <li class="collection-item">Leave the keys on the desk.</li>
                <li class="collection-item">Throw away any large trash items in the trash receptacle next to the driveway.</li>
                <li class="collection-item">Leave used towels and linens on the bed.</li>
                <li class="collection-item">Check drawers and outlets for chargers.</li>
                <li class="collection-item">Exit through the front door, don't worry about locking up.</li>
                <li class="collection-item">Remove food from your pantry and refrigerator shelves.</li>
                <li class="collection-item">Remove any items from the bathroom and shower area.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
